{"tid":2035121,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘3米長糞渠飛墮地面毀3車　車內司機頸痛","createTime":"2020-05-25T16:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T03:37:43.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"53371b852ae83a78e7f65840b57403f01adb84db","tid":2035121,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/photo/bkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200525224502\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200525224502&h=841e5097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘發生墮渠毀車傷人意外。今晚(25日)8時許，海濱道177號海裕工業中心外牆，一條約3米長糞渠疑失修突然鬆脫，並折斷飛墮而下。期間，糞渠擊中旁邊偉業街174號建德豐工業大樓外牆一部冷氣機，再連同冷氣機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一併墮落於兩幢大廈之間的後巷，砸毀3輛汽車，包括客貨車、貨車及私家車。警方接報趕抵，圍封現場調查，聯絡大廈業主了解情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/photo/bkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_02b.jpg?20200525224502\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20200525224502&h=dc00f9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓林客貨車司機表示，事發一刻他正在車內，事後感到頸痛，左車身被砸凹。貨車及私家車姓<span style=\"color: red;\">陳司機稱，他將貨車停泊於上址後，打算再駕駛私家車離去，惟在抹車時發生意外，對此感到無奈。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/photo/bkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_05b.jpg?20200525224502\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_05b.jpg%3F20200525224502&h=ed18cec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n客貨車司機(左)頸痛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/photo/bkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_07b.jpg?20200525224502\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_07b.jpg%3F20200525224502&h=342302c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防到場調查。"},{"pid":"778ce4aa4f2a31ae5a400938e8c1cb676f4758de","tid":2035121,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"警方圍封現場調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/photo/bkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_06b.jpg?20200525224502\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200525215547422-0525_00822_001_06b.jpg%3F20200525224502&h=b50667e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圍封見到，邊個係警方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782f796565d028edc385ac569067777c3f8966b7","tid":2035121,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"中國製造嗎?"},{"pid":"c39192662d1a1c9dbc19306739021276518483e2","tid":2035121,"uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"原來屎渠入面有咁多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e2ece35dcab1c759ff864e22989442a00afe51","tid":2035121,"uid":209773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c39192662d1a1c9dbc19306739021276518483e2","tid":2035121,"uid":66365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"原來屎渠入面有咁多屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbef8618e8272521aedc22df412fba3c322ada85","tid":2035121,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:40:37.000Z","msg":"哪裡來的屎呀？"},{"pid":"6e34ee8aab4bb37c3588aef57ed92a8efc28eaa1","tid":2035121,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"有刺客"},{"pid":"f49